untuk memeriksanya.

00:15:40.200 --> 00:15:41.088
Panggil doktor.

00:15:41.248 --> 00:15:41.840
ya.

00:15:43.880 --> 00:15:45.520
Panggil doktor!

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:54.560
Salam sejahtera, Tuanku.

00:15:54.680 --> 00:15:55.440
Doktor Liu,

00:15:55.880 --> 00:15:58.320
periksa nadi Lady Shen.

00:15:58.760 --> 00:15:59.960
Ya, Tuanku.

00:16:24.560 --> 00:16:25.320
Tuanku,

00:16:25.520 --> 00:16:27.360
Nadi Lady Shen menunjukkan
ketegangan seperti rentetan

00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:28.440
dan lembab,

00:16:28.440 --> 00:16:30.000
menunjukkan genangan qi hati

00:16:30.040 --> 00:16:31.360
dan ketidakseimbangan limpa-perut.

00:16:31.560 --> 00:16:33.240
Makanan berminyak yang berlebihan

00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:35.440
telah menyebabkan pengumpulan haba lembap.

00:16:35.640 --> 00:16:38.120
Oleh itu, kembung perut dan loya.

00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:41.000
Puan Shen, awak sentiasa lemah,

00:16:41.200 --> 00:16:42.080
dan masih kurang sihat.

00:16:42.360 --> 00:16:43.800
Awak patut jaga diri awak.

00:16:47.160 --> 00:16:48.640
Keprihatinan Tuanku menghormati saya, Tuanku.

00:16:48.960 --> 00:16:51.960
Saya akan lebih berhati-hati mulai sekarang.

00:16:53.560 --> 00:16:54.360
Doktor Liu,

00:16:54.920 --> 00:16:55.840
adakah anda pasti

00:16:56.080 --> 00:16:59.240
Lady Shen tidak muntah
kerana dia mengandung?

00:17:01.080 --> 00:17:02.840
Saya memeriksa Nadi Cun-Guan-Chi tiga kali

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:05.440
dengan palpasi yang mendalam dan cetek.

00:17:05.760 --> 00:17:06.840
nadi Lady Shen

00:17:07.080 --> 00:17:08.640
menunjukkan meridian Chong dan Ren biasa

00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:10.080
tanpa tanda janin.

00:17:10.680 --> 00:17:11.560
Puan Shen

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:12.840
tidak hamil.

00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:14.200
Doktor Liu,

00:17:14.360 --> 00:17:15.560
adakah anda meneliti dengan teliti?

00:17:16.080 --> 00:17:16.880
Tuanku,

00:17:17.120 --> 00:17:18.480
peperiksaan saya teliti.

00:17:18.760 --> 00:17:20.640
Saya pasti Lady Shen tidak hamil.

00:17:20.880 --> 00:17:21.560
Puan Shen,

00:17:21.840 --> 00:17:23.360
beritahu Baginda sendiri sekarang.

00:17:25.400 --> 00:17:26.280
kamu pembantu rumah yang hina!

00:17:26.600 --> 00:17:28.280
Mengapa membuat spekulasi
di hadapan Baginda?

00:17:29.040 --> 00:17:30.080
Tidak mempercayai doktor?

00:17:31.040 --> 00:17:32.160
Tuanku.

00:17:35.480 --> 00:17:36.640
Saya pasti tidak hamil.

00:17:37.360 --> 00:17:39.520
Doktor Liu sudah memeriksa nadi saya.

00:17:40.360 --> 00:17:43.080
Namun seorang pembantu istana yang hina seperti kamu
berulang kali mempersoalkannya.

00:17:43.360 --> 00:17:44.760
Apakah niat sebenar anda?

00:17:45.560 --> 00:17:48.600
Adakah anda membayangkan saya berani
menipu Baginda?

00:17:53.480 --> 00:17:54.160
Tuanku.

00:17:54.600 --> 00:17:55.360
Puan Shen

00:17:55.360 --> 00:17:57.520
tak berani
minum arak tadi.

00:17:57.960 --> 00:18:01.040
Saya pasti dia hamil.

00:18:01.640 --> 00:18:02.840
Tetapi dia sedang dimanipulasi

00:18:02.840 --> 00:18:03.560
dan tidak boleh bercakap.

00:18:04.040 --> 00:18:04.920
Tolong siasat!

